ussing these topics.<BR><BR>I have gone through the homam manual provided b=
y Sri.Narasimhaji and the video of a homam being performed and have the fol=
lowing observations to make.<BR><BR>1. As per rules laid out by srouta and =
gruhya sutras which describe the preocedures for various rituals, any yajna=
 (homam) can only be a vikruti of the darsapoornamasa (which is the prakrut=
i of all yajnas).<BR><BR>2. All steps in darsapoornamasa should be there in=
