nding at NE corner (Eshaadi eeshaantam).<BR><BR>8 Patraasadanam or keeping =
the vessels and ladles used in the vessel above darbha is missing.<BR><BR>9=
.Prokshanee samskaram and prokshanam for purification of the utensils is mi=
ssing.<BR><BR>10. Patra samskaram or purifying the utensils is missing.<BR>=
